name: Sacrifice
description:
It made me realize that there is no such a thing like “FREE” in this world, everything you earn in your life, you acquire, comes with the price, you have to sacrifice something to be able to earn it, not only material like money but it could be a TIME. To be smart you sacrifice your time to learn, to be healthy you sacrifice your desire to eat junk food, even tho as simple as moving an object from here to there you sacrifice your energy to be able to do it. So my point is, everything in this world, every action you have made, it comes with the prices.

Blue Version
